Q17. Write a code to take a number as an input from the user and check if the number is odd or even.
A)num=input("Enter the number:")
  if(num%2==0):
      print("Even")
  else:
      print("Odd")

Q18. What are boolean operator?
A)Boolean Operators are simple words (AND, OR, NOT or AND NOT) and gives boolean as ouput after performing the operations.

Q19. What will the output of the following?
1 or 0---> 1

0 and 0--->0

True and False and True ---->False

1 or 0 or 0--->1

